# Cloudflare Pages Redirects
# ==========================
# Syntax: <source> <destination> <status>
# 200 = internal rewrite (preserves URL)
#
# /apply is handled by functions/apply.js Pages Function
# /list  is handled by functions/list.js Pages Function
# /rally is handled by functions/rally.js Pages Function
# /apply/api/* is handled by functions/apply/api/[[catchall]].js
#
# No redirect rules needed — Pages Functions handle all routing.